## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Push Script (Tạo Collection với Quantization)

#### [MODIFY] [push_sqlite_to_qdrant.py](file:///c:/Law%20Chatbot/data_pipelines/vector_rag/push_sqlite_to_qdrant.py)

Thay đổi hàm `ensure_collection()` để bật Scalar Quantization + tối ưu HNSW:

```python
# TRƯỚC
client.create_collection(
    collection_name=collection_name,
    vectors_config={
        "dense": models.VectorParams(
            size=dim,
            distance=models.Distance.COSINE,
        ),
    },
    sparse_vectors_config={
        "sparse": models.SparseVectorParams(),
    },
)

# SAU
client.create_collection(
    collection_name=collection_name,
    vectors_config={
        "dense": models.VectorParams(
            size=dim,
            distance=models.Distance.COSINE,
            quantization_config=models.ScalarQuantization(
                scalar=models.ScalarQuantizationConfig(
                    type=models.ScalarType.INT8,
                    quantile=0.99,
                    always_ram=True,
                ),
            ),
        ),
    },
    sparse_vectors_config={
        "sparse": models.SparseVectorParams(),
    },
    optimizers_config=models.OptimizersConfigDiff(
        indexing_threshold=20000,
    ),
)
```

Thêm flag `--quantize` CLI.

---

### Component 2: Backend Retriever (Search Params cho Rescore)

#### [MODIFY] [retriever.py](file:///c:/Law%20Chatbot/backend/app/services/retriever.py)

Thêm `search_params` vào `query_points()` call trong `_hybrid_search()` để bật rescoring:

```python
# Thêm vào Qdrant query_points call
result = await self._qdrant.query_points(
    collection_name=self._collection,
    prefetch=[...],  # giữ nguyên
    query=qmodels.FusionQuery(fusion=qmodels.Fusion.RRF),
    limit=top_k,
    with_payload=True,
    search_params=qmodels.SearchParams(
        quantization=qmodels.QuantizationSearchParams(
            rescore=True,       # rescore bằng float32 gốc
            oversampling=1.5,   # lấy 1.5x candidates trước khi rescore
        ),
    ),
)
```

---

### Component 3: Docker Compose (Tăng RAM Qdrant)

#### [MODIFY] [docker-compose.yml](file:///c:/Law%20Chatbot/backend/docker-compose.yml)

```yaml
# Qdrant
deploy:
  resources:
    limits:
      memory: 5G    # 3.5G → 5G (cần cho SQ + HNSW sau rechunk)
```

---

### Component 4: Kaggle Notebook (Tăng Chunk Size — CHỈ KHI Q1 = CÓ)

#### [MODIFY] [dataset_replace_kaggle.ipynb](file:///c:/Law%20Chatbot/data_pipelines/kaggle_pipeline/dataset_replace_kaggle.ipynb)

Thay đổi `PipelineConfig`:
```python
chunk_size_chars: int = 2400      # 1200 → 2400
chunk_overlap_chars: int = 200    # 150 → 200
min_chunk_chars: int = 300        # 200 → 300
```

Sau khi chạy xong trên Kaggle → download SQLite files → chạy `push_sqlite_to_qdrant.py --reset`.

